# Switch

# Default

Code
<template>
  <Example>
    <template #demos>
        <sf-switch v-model="value" on="Sim" off="Não"/>
    </template>
  </Example>
</template>

<script>
export default {
	data() {
		return {
			value: null
		}
	},
}
</script>

# Custom Value

null
Code
<template>
  <Example>
    <template #demos>
		<sf-switch v-model="value" val="Luis Eduardo" label="Luis Eduardo"/>
    </template>

    <template #result>
  	  {{ value ? value : 'null' }}
    </template>
  </Example>
</template>

<script>

export default {
	data() {
		return {
			value: null,
		}
	}
}
</script>

# Object Value

null
Code
<template>
  <Example>
    <template #demos>
		<sf-switch v-model="value" :val="obj" label="Luis Eduardo"/>
    </template>

    <template #result>
  	  {{ value ? value : 'null' }}
    </template>
  </Example>
</template>

<script>

export default {
	data() {
		return {
			obj: { id: 1, name: 'Eduardo' },
			value: null,
		}
	}
}
</script>

# Array Value

[ "Eduardo" ]
Code
<template>
  <Example>
    <template #demos>
		<sf-switch v-model="arrayItems" val="Luis" label="Luis"/>
		<sf-switch v-model="arrayItems" val="Eduardo" label="Eduardo"/>
		<sf-switch v-model="arrayItems" val="Miranda" label="Miranda"/>
		<sf-switch v-model="arrayItems" val="Ferreira" label="Ferreira"/>
    </template>

    <template #result>
  	  {{ arrayItems }}
    </template>
  </Example>
</template>

<script>

export default {
	data() {
		return {
			arrayItems: ['Eduardo'],
		}
	}
}
</script>

# Array Objects

[ { "id": 1, "name": "Thays" } ]
Code
<template>
  <Example>
    <template #demos>
		<sf-switch v-model="objectArray" :val="thays" keyId="id"  :label="thays.name"/>
		<sf-switch v-model="objectArray" :val="ferreira" keyId="id" :label="ferreira.name"/>
		<sf-switch v-model="objectArray" :val="dos" keyId="id" :label="dos.name "/>
		<sf-switch v-model="objectArray" :val="santos" keyId="id" :label="santos.name"/>
    </template>

    <template #result>
  	  {{ JSON.stringify(objectArray, null, 2) }}
    </template>
  </Example>
</template>

<script>

export default {
	data() {
		return {
			thays: {
				id: 1,
				name: 'Thays'
			},
			ferreira: {
				id: 2,
				name: 'Ferreira'
			},
			dos: {
				id: 3,
				name: 'dos'
			},
			santos: {
				id: 4,
				name: 'Santos'
			},
			objectArray: [{
				id: 1,
				name: 'Thays'
			}]
		}
	}
}
</script>

# Color

Code
<template>
  <Example>
    <template #demos>
      <sf-switch v-model="value" label="Default"/>
      <sf-switch v-model="value" label="Primary" color="primary"/>
      <sf-switch v-model="value" label="Success" color="success"/>
      <sf-switch v-model="value" label="Warn" color="warn"/>
      <sf-switch v-model="value" label="Danger" color="danger"/>
    </template>
  </Example>
</template>

<script>
export default {
	data() {
		return {
			value: false
		}
	}
}
</script>
